j25_myarturia_preset_bank_audio.title: Marello
j25_myarturia_preset_bank_audio.description: A downtempo track with strong eerie feeling, taking advantage of the various filters modes, on board effects and voice parameters to fill the stereo width and audio spectrum.

j25_myarturia_preset_bank_audio.title: Sunset
j25_myarturia_preset_bank_audio.description: This minimalist demo features a light lead, the \"Mountain Echo\" preset, and a filter glide effect which take you to an other dimension.

j25_myarturia_preset_bank_audio.title: Sommore Groove
j25_myarturia_preset_bank_audio.description: This is a short but groovy house track. Everything comes from the Mini V, except for the drums sounds.

j25_myarturia_preset_bank_audio.title: The V Sunset
j25_myarturia_preset_bank_audio.description: The demo \"The V Sunset\" perfectly describes the state of mind in which I made these presets. A deep yet light house track!

j25_myarturia_preset_bank_audio.title: Chrimbrus
j25_myarturia_preset_bank_audio.description: Beatless demo using two instances of Synclavier V modulating the Timbre Chorus parameter. Presets are Moon Chord and Sun Fall.

j25_myarturia_preset_bank_audio.title: Jupiter Voices
j25_myarturia_preset_bank_audio.description: Dreamy electro tracks using two instances of Jup-8 V. Presets are Etherpad and Orbits.

j25_myarturia_preset_bank_audio.title: Centeize
j25_myarturia_preset_bank_audio.description: This slow and minimalistic track is featuring a bass made with the \"Chica-go\" preset from the Prophet V, the \"Drunk Cats in Space\" keys and the \"LITM Torn\" patch from the Farfisa V.

j25_myarturia_preset_bank_audio.title: Ilova
j25_myarturia_preset_bank_audio.description: This deep track is made using 2 instances of Synclavier V with the Deep Bell presets and one instance of Prophet V using the Argento Pingers patch.\n

j25_myarturia_preset_bank_audio.title: Mini V
j25_myarturia_preset_bank_audio.description: Emotive lead, sun-drenched synths, classic drum machine beats in a chilled retro driven sound.

j25_myarturia_preset_bank_audio.title: Prophet V
j25_myarturia_preset_bank_audio.description: Outrun-style bass with 80s lead and chord driven chords jam packed for a classic inspired sound.
